## Layout

```
apps/web/   — Vite + React 19 + TS + Tailwind v4 (frontend)
apps/api/   — uv + FastAPI + Pydantic v2 + SQLAlchemy 2 async (backend)
.helix/     — manifest + helixcli state. Don't edit by hand.
```

## Commands

```bash
# One-shot: deps for both apps + start both dev servers in background
helixcli install
helixcli up      # http://localhost:5173 + http://localhost:8000
helixcli down    # stop them

# Or by hand
npm install                                       # workspace root
npm run dev --workspace apps/web                  # frontend
( cd apps/api && uv sync && uv run fastapi dev app/main.py )  # backend

# Regenerate TS types from FastAPI's OpenAPI schema (backend must be up)
npm run gen:types --workspace apps/web
```

See `.helix/README.md` for what helixcli has scaffolded so far.
